data.description:
Welcome to 7305 Werkbund Way, a charming two-bedroom, two-bathroom condo nestled in the heart of South Knoxville, TN. This beautiful residence boasts an open floor plan with cathedral ceilings in the living room, creating an airy and spacious ambiance. Warm up by the cozy gas fireplace on chilly evenings, adding to the inviting atmosphere.
The primary bedroom is generously sized, featuring a large ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet, offering ample storage space for your belongings. Step outside to your private back porch, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or evening relaxation in a serene setting.
This low maintenance condo also includes an oversized two-car garage, providing plenty of room for parking and additional storage. The large flat yard surrounding the property offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening.
Situated in a private location at the back of the neighborhood, 7305 Werkbund Way offers peace and tranquility. Yet, it's just minutes away from the University of Tennessee, UT Medical Center, downtown Knoxville, the airport, and numerous outdoor parks and activities.
Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a cozy retreat in a convenient and desirable location. Schedule your viewing today and experience all that this lovely condo has to offer!
